---
title: Smoky Chorizo and Refried Black Bean Tacos with Wedges, Rocket Slaw and Cheese
description: A twist on refried beans, we're using black beans instead of pinto beans and stirring through chorizo and smoky base paste, made with smoked paprika and smoked salt, to bring rich smoky flavour to your dish. Pile your tacos with the beans, slaw and cheese for a hearty dinner.
